entry.para:
If no budgets exist yet, just open a new budget. If only one budget exists, create a copy of it;
                      otherwise user selects one to copy. If a copy is made, then the copy is opened
                      in a new tab.

sect2.para:
La scheda Generali permette l’accesso alle informazioni di base del conto. Fornisce un modo di collegare il conto alle informazioni sulle azioni se si tratta di un tipo di conto per la valuta, per i fondi comuni o per le azioni. Qui, il conto può anche essere marcato come segnaposto; viene inoltre mostrato se il conto è identificato come relativo alle tasse (che è configurato attraverso il menu
ModificaOpzioni resoconto tasse
).

The Tax Related check-box means that an account has been flagged to be included in the Tax Schedule Report. This flag is only displayed on the Edit Account dialog and is set in the Income Tax Information dialog (
EditTax Report Options
). See the Tax Schedule Report and TXF Export section in Reports Chapter ().

If a relevant price is available in the price database (see
          ) the Exchange Rate will
          have that as a default entry.

Invoices can also be printed from the main window by selecting
ReportsBusiness Reports Printable Invoice
from the main menu. The resulting report window states that no valid invoice is selected. To select the invoice to print:

row.entry:
Other costs not specified on other lines of Schedule C, such as: Clean-fuel
vehicles and refueling property; Donations to business organizations;
Educational expenses; Environmental cleanup costs; Impairment-related expenses;
Interview expense allowances; Licenses and regulatory fees; Moving machinery;
Outplacement services; Penalties and fines you pay for late performance or
nonperformance of a contract; Subscriptions to trade or professional
publications.
